Title.Name: Top Content

Item.Name: Pageviews
Item.HelpMsg: The total number of pages viewed. Repeated views of a single page are counted.

Item.Name: Unique Pageviews
Item.HelpMsg: The number of visits during which one or more of these pages was viewed.

Item.Name: Avg. Time on Page
Item.HelpMsg: The average amount of time visitors spent viewing this set of pages or page.

Item.Name: Bounce Rate
Item.HelpMsg: The percentage of single page visits resulting from this set of pages or page.

Item.Name: % Exit
Item.HelpMsg: The percentage of site exits that occurred from this set of pages or page.

Item.Name: $ Index
Item.HelpMsg: The average value of this page or set of pages. $Index is (Ecommerce revenue + Total Goal Value) divided by Pageviews for the page(s).
